frames.caption: An elderly man in traditional Chinese attire stands solemnly, holding a staff with a large golden snake draped over his shoulders. Red lanterns and floral decorations form a rich, cultural backdrop.
frames.description: The scene captures a traditional and ceremonial setting, where an elderly man is depicted with a sense of wisdom and authority. The presence of the snake and the red lanterns suggests themes of tradition and symbolism.
